# Optional — URL of a server-side proxy that forwards Converse chats to Anthropic
# and returns a { native, roman, en, feedback } reply (see README → "Live tutor").
# Leave it unset to run the Converse tutor in scripted demo mode (no backend, no key).
#
# The Anthropic API key lives ONLY on the proxy. Never put a key in this file,
# in the frontend, or anywhere in the repo — anything prefixed VITE_ is bundled
# into the public client build.
VITE_TUTOR_PROXY_URL=
